article_title: Foul play not suspected in Raleigh death
article_text:

— Police on Friday said they have found no evidence of foul play in the death of a man whose body was found Thursday afternoon in Raleigh.

The body of Anthony Bowen Watson, 29, of Raleigh, was found in a wooded area off the end of Belmont Drive in southeast Raleigh.

No other information about the case has been released.
